snippet.textDisplay:
Seriously, the opening was so irritating, that after backing vocalist starts doing "Turu Turu" it was almost someone pinching in your ears. And then "Mer Meri Meri" again... Rizwan could have done a lot more after what we have seen him doing at Nescafe Basement. Dozens of rendition of this song can be found and it just an other addition to that wasteful list. On a whim Sara too lacks in this songs, not everything is about vocals and hitting notes, it just didn't suit her. With an addition dumb-shit music overpowers their voices and kills every essence of this Kalam .  Such a waste of money on this song. 

Score: Composition 4/10 Singing 6/10 Overall 5/10
